members.name: CryptoKey.type
members.description: Returns an enumerated value representing the type of the key, a secret key (for symmetric algorithm), a public or a private key (for an asymmetric algorithm)

members.name: CryptoKey.extractable
members.description: Returns a Boolean indicating if the raw information may be exported to the application or not.

members.name: CryptoKey.algorithm
members.description: Returns an opaque object representing a particular cipher the key has to be used with.

members.name: CryptoKey.usages
members.description: Returns an array of enumerated values indicating what the key can be used for.
